com.mappedin.sdk

Class ImageCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mappedin.sdk.ImageCollection

  • public class ImageCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of references to images of various sizes. Use get(int, Context) to get an image of that size or greater (in display units multiplied by display scale). Gives you the URL of the image you need to download.
